snippet.title: Kingdom Come: Deliverance - Royal Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
The Royal Edition includes the base game in its enhanced version as well as all free and paid DLCs released so far. Enjoy the full Kingdom Come: Deliverance experience including:

– Treasures of the Past
– From The Ashes
– The Amorous Adventures of the bold Sir Hans Capon
– Band of Bastards
– A Woman’s Lot

Choose your weapon & Get the Game now!
